Package supermarket.domain.controllers

Class StoreController

java.lang.Object
supermarket.domain.controllers.StoreController
public class StoreController extends Object
Manages multiple stores in the supermarket domain. The StoreController class allows creating, deleting, and managing stores, as well as handling shelves and products within those stores.
